OL,3,CFamilies of Nottingham attacks victims
OL,4,Cexpect public inquiry to be confirmed
OL,6,FThree other people were seriously
OL,7,Finjured when Calocane, took Mr Coates
OL,8,Fvan and drove at them in Nottingham.
OL,10,FThe families of victims said they
OL,11,Frecognise the 'gravity' of their
OL,12,Fmeeting with the Prime Minister, the
OL,13,FHome Secretary, the Health Secretary
OL,14,Fand the Attorney General today
OL,15,F(February 12th).
OL,17,FEmma Webber, the mother of Barnaby
OL,18,FWebber, said she expected an inquiry
OL,19,Fto be confirmed during the meeting at
OL,20,FNumber 10, describing it as a
OL,21,F"watershed moment for this case".
