OL,6,FMrs Webber said: "The families
OL,7,Frecognise the gravity and importance
OL,8,Fof their meeting with the Prime
OL,9,FMinister, Home Secretary, Health
OL,10,FSecretary, Attorney General and
OL,11,Fvictim's minister on Wednesday.
OL,13,F"From it they expect to receive
OL,14,Fconfirmation that the promised public
OL,15,Finquiry will be a statutory one.
OL,17,F"That a suitable start date within
OL,18,F2025 is set and terms to be agreed for
OL,19,Fwho will lead it and how it will be
OL,20,Fled.
