OL,6,F"It must have the 'teeth' it needs to
OL,7,Fensure full transparency and compel
OL,8,Fagencies and individuals, involved to
OL,9,Ftake the stand and tell the truth.
OL,11,F"The Webber, Coates and Kumar families
OL,12,Fhave nothing to hide, defend or
OL,13,Fembellish. They expect nothing other
OL,14,Fthan this from those who must now be
OL,15,Fbrought forward.
OL,17,F"It must be a watershed moment for
OL,18,Fthis case, for public safety and for
OL,19,Fthe health service and criminal
OL,20,Fjustice system."
