OL,6,FDowning Street previously said Sir
OL,7,FKeir is committed to a judge-led
OL,8,Finquiry and has not ruled out a public
OL,9,Finquiry with full statutory powers.
OL,11,FTheir scheduled meeting with the PM
OL,12,Ffollows the publication of NHS
OL,13,FEngland's report into the mental
OL,14,Fhealth care received by Calocane in
OL,15,Fthe lead up to the attacks on February
OL,16,F5th.
