OL,6,FThe families of the victims held a
OL,7,Fpress conference in London in reaction
OL,8,Fto the NHS Nottinghamshire
OL,9,Fhealthcare's report which details the
OL,10,Fcontact Calocane had with mental
OL,11,Fhealth services.
OL,13,FWhat did the report say?
OL,15,FThe 302 report, published today,
OL,16,Fidentified a series of failings by the
OL,17,Ftrust including that the killer was
OL,18,Fnot forced to take long- lasting anti-
OL,19,Fpsychotic medication because he
OL,20,Fdisliked needles.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
