OL,6,FIt also found that Calocane's care
OL,7,Frisk "was not fully understood,
OL,8,Fmanaged, documented or communicated"
OL,9,Fand that there were missed
OL,10,Fopportunities to take more assertive
OL,11,Faction towards Calocane's care.
OL,13,FThe review said other patients cared
OL,14,Ffor by Nottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,15,FFoundation Trust also committed
OL,16,F"extremely serious" acts of violence `
OL,17,Fincluding stabbings ` between 2019 and
OL,18,F2023.
