OL,6,FThe NHS took the decision to publish
OL,7,Fthe report in full after originally
OL,8,Fsaying that only a redacted version
OL,9,Fwould be released because of
OL,10,F"protection legislation relating to
OL,11,Fpatient information".
OL,13,FDr Jessica Sokolov, regional medical
OL,14,Fdirector at NHS England (Midlands),
OL,15,Fsaid: "It's clear the system got it
OL,16,Fwrong, including the NHS, and the
OL,17,Fconsequences of when this happens can
OL,18,Fbe devastating.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
